v0.1.3

- all actions now have requirement tooltip
- bug fix: only sheriffs can open jail doors
- if someone asks about village leader, that person is known to the performer
- rework dialogue system to allow list of subjects
- add ctrl-left mouse click functionality to talk
- add meat and butcher action
- people become ghouls by eating human flesh
- add gradient to screens
- add icons to all magic spells

v0.1.2

- add tooltips for several actions
- kiss and sex action are only possible on non-hostile persons
- fix right-click to cover entire worldobject instead of only top-left corner
- reworked inventory dialog
- add background music
- make it possible to assign action to left mouse button
- improve arena image
- add iron greaves, iron greatsword, iron shield, iron axe and iron greataxe

v0.1.1

- brawls can now be fought for money
- brawls should be unarmed, using a weapon ends the brawl
- add organization overview screen
- show a red line over targets of the player - character indicating hit points
- player is now notified when creature type changes
- add arena functionality
- add tooltips to start screens and info screens
- rework inventory dialog

v0.1.0

- bug fix: npcs only run from enemy if it is close
- bug fix: research multiple turns isn't available when all spells are known
- add fish, fishing pole, fisher profession
- add magic spell Lightning Bolt
- add weight, encumbrance and burden and feather magic spells
- add inventory actions (eat, drink) to inventory dialog
- bug fix: cannot talk with mindless undead anymore
- bug fix: equipped items which are removed from inventory are no longer equipped
- npcs now share knowledge when socializing
- add brawling
- add logo for window icons
- commoner attributes are now generated randomly
- constitution governs starting hit points

